Pick up the black mug from the box.
Walk around the table and head left to walk down the passage to reach the cabinet on the left.
Put the mug in the cabinet.
Turn around and turn left to head down the passage and turn left to enter the bathroom on the right and face the sink.
Pick up the mug from the sink.
Turn around to exit the bathroom and turn left to the end of the passage and turn right to walk down the passage and turn right to reach the cabinet on the left.
Put the mug in the cabinet with the other mug.

Grab the mug.
Get out of the bathroom. At the end of the hallway, turn right. Enter the entrance that are in the middle. Go to the cabinet with doors.
Open the first cabinet. Put the mug in. Close the cabinet.

Pick up the mug from the sofa.
Step out from the sofa and head to a corridor that is on the opposite side of the room to the right, and stop when you are at the first cabinet to your right.
Place the mug inside the cabinet.
